At Indian and Pacific Oceans
N. tenuipes
occurs from the Agulhas Bank and Mozambique Strait up to Taiwan , Japan , New Caledonia , Hawaii, Vanuatu , Fiji and Tonga Islands at depths of 630–3075 m (usually 1400–1700 m ) (
Burukovsky 1991
;
2000 a
;
2002 c
;
2012
;
2013
). In the Eastern Pacific this species is recorded at the East Pacific rise (
12 ° 45 'N
/
